# FILE: halabFreelance/freelanceOnboarding/freelanceOnboarding.desc
# ROLE: Professional Entry Gate & Monetization Logic
# ROUTE: /freelance/onboarding
# ACCOUNT: Student only — Business freelancers register via /auth/register → businessType: 'freelancer'
# THEME: Dark · step wizard · gradient progress indicator

## ROUTING LOGIC
- If accountType === 'student' AND isFreelancer === false → show this onboarding
- If accountType === 'business' AND businessType === 'freelancer' → redirect to /business (already have access)
- If not logged in → redirect to /auth/login

## 1. HERO (Top Fold)
- HEADLINE: "حوّل مهاراتك الأكاديمية إلى مصدر دخل"
- SUBTEXT: "Challenge Every Day." — italic gradient-text
- IDENTITY CHECK: small card showing current user name + "مستقل طلابي" badge preview
- ALERT (if !isVerified): rose warning — "يجب التحقق من هويتك الجامعية أولاً" + [رفع الهوية] button

## 2. STEP WIZARD (3 Steps)
- PROGRESS: 3 dots connected by line · active = gradient-bg dot

- STEP 1: TERMS OF SERVICE
  - Scrollable bordered box with platform terms
  - Commission fee: 5% to HalabUnver
  - Checkbox: [✅ أوافق على ميثاق HalabUnver المهني]

- STEP 2: SKILL ALIGNMENT
  - Shows tags pulled from student's academic profile
  - Editable tag confirmation: [MERN] [Linux] [Pentesting]
  - Add/remove skills before publishing

- STEP 3: SUBSCRIPTION FEE
  - "وصول مركز المستقلين: 5 دولار / شهر (أو ما يعادله بالليرة)"
  - ShamCash payment instructions
  - [💳 انتقل إلى المحفظة لإتمام الدفع] → /dashboard/wallet with metadata tag type: "FREELANCE_SUB"

## 3. PUBLIC PROFILE PREVIEW
- Live preview of how freelancer will appear in /freelance/leaderboard
- [✏️ تعديل النبذة العامة] → /freelance/profile/me

## 4. ESCROW EDUCATION
- Bordered info box explaining escrow logic
- [📖 قواعد الضمان المالي] → popup with security protocol

## 5. STICKY STATUS BAR
- PRE-PAYMENT: 🔴 "وصول محدود — أكمل الدفع لفتح الإمكانيات الكاملة"
- POST-PAYMENT (pending admin confirm): 🟡 "قيد التفعيل — جاري التحقق من دفعتك"
- POST-CONFIRM: 🟢 "مرحباً بك في سوق المستقلين!" → sets isFreelancer: true
